Capital Markets

Company Overview of Fort Pitt Capital Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Fort Pitt Capital Group Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, typically high net-worth individuals. It also manages accounts for investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client focused equity portfolios. It also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. Fort Pitt Capital Group was founded in 1995 and is based in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania with an additional office in Naples, Florida. As of October 1, 2015, Fort Pi...
Fort Pitt Capital Group Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals, typically high net-worth individuals. It also manages accounts for investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client focused equity portfolios. It also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. Fort Pitt Capital Group was founded in 1995 and is based in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania with an additional office in Naples, Florida. As of October 1, 2015, Fort Pitt Capital Group, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Focus Financial Partners, LLC.
Detailed Description


