Fort Pitt Capital Group, Inc.



 OVERVIEW



Date Founded


1995




Headquarters


Foster Plaza 10, 680 Andersen Drive, Pittsburgh, PA 15220-2759




Employees (Worldwide)


31




Industries


Investment Services & Portfolio Management




Company Description


Fort Pitt is a US large-cap growth manager, investing primarily in the finance sector. They also invest in high grade bonds. The Fort Pitt Total Return Fund invests across market-caps with a median market-cap of $20 billion. Company value is measured by ROE and stock valuation is measured by p/e ratio. The Fund buys companies whose p/e ratios are close to ROE. The Fund holds about 50 positions and offers little foreign exposure.




Website


http://www.fortpittcapital.com/






